abilities.name: Earth Spike
abilities.description: Rock spikes burst from the earth along a straight path. Enemy units are hurled into the air, then are stunned and take damage when they fall.

abilities.name: Hex
abilities.description: Transforms an enemy unit into a harmless beast, with all special abilities disabled.

abilities.name: Mana Drain
abilities.description: CHANNELED - Absorbs the magical energies of a target enemy unit by taking mana from it every second.

abilities.name: Finger of Death
abilities.description: Rips at an enemy unit, trying to turn it inside-out. Deals massive damage and grows stronger with each life it consumes. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.
abilities.upgrade_description: Increases damage. Decreases cooldown. Finger of Death hits all units in a small area.

talents.name: +2 Mana Drain Multi Target
talents.description: Automatically targets additional enemy units with a mana pool within 400 distance around the original target.
